WEBVTT

01:43.070 --> 01:46.060
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.120 --> 01:48.990
[Episode 14]

01:50.509 --> 01:51.170
Professor Yu.

01:51.259 --> 01:52.160
You're not having a class soon, are you?

01:52.630 --> 01:54.050
There's 20 minutes left. What's wrong?

01:54.080 --> 01:55.170
I want to ask you something.

01:55.350 --> 01:56.340
Have you read this book?

01:58.070 --> 01:59.080
"Hiroshima Mon Amour"?

01:59.500 --> 02:00.910
Why are you reading this book?

02:01.830 --> 02:03.270
Have you fallen in love with someone

02:03.300 --> 02:04.530
you shouldn't have?

02:04.560 --> 02:05.790
Don't make fun of me.

02:06.630 --> 02:07.710
It's just

02:07.840 --> 02:09.380
I've been investigating a case,

02:09.550 --> 02:10.770
and there's been no clue.

02:11.150 --> 02:12.950
But recently, I found that

02:13.030 --> 02:14.380
the girl involved

02:14.380 --> 02:15.430
had been

02:15.430 --> 02:16.910
borrowing this book

02:16.950 --> 02:17.840
from the school library when she was in college.

02:17.870 --> 02:18.840
She borrowed it many times

02:19.310 --> 02:20.390
and never returned it in the end.

02:20.079 --> 02:21.880
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

02:20.510 --> 02:21.750
I was thinking,

02:23.500 --> 02:25.530
if a college girl

02:25.790 --> 02:28.030
reads this book every day...

02:28.730 --> 02:29.760
I don't know.

02:29.870 --> 02:31.570
Can you analyze this girl's

02:31.640 --> 02:33.120
psychological state

02:33.590 --> 02:34.670
from this perspective?

02:37.650 --> 02:39.230
"Hiroshima Mon Amour"

02:39.270 --> 02:41.220
is mainly about how

02:41.250 --> 02:42.310
the heroine fell in love uncontrollably

02:42.329 --> 02:43.430
with the male lead under the background of war.

02:43.800 --> 02:45.810
Besides, both of them had their own families,

02:45.910 --> 02:46.880
and the male lead

02:46.910 --> 02:47.990
was even an invader.

02:48.190 --> 02:49.230
At that time,

02:49.270 --> 02:50.510
it was against common ethics

02:50.700 --> 02:52.650
and even despised by the world.

02:53.670 --> 02:54.840
If the victim

02:54.870 --> 02:55.720
projected so much emotion

02:55.750 --> 02:57.500
on this book,

02:57.900 --> 02:58.550
it's very likely that

02:58.590 --> 02:59.280
she also fell in love with

02:59.310 --> 03:00.310
someone she shouldn't have.

03:01.390 --> 03:03.020
The other person

03:03.070 --> 03:04.010
might have major differences

03:04.070 --> 03:04.800
from her

03:04.830 --> 03:06.390
in terms of status, class, and stance.

03:07.070 --> 03:08.080
Or

03:08.150 --> 03:09.590
their relationship

03:09.610 --> 03:11.300
could not be known to outsiders

03:11.410 --> 03:13.270
or accepted by the world.

03:15.280 --> 03:16.240
That's my speculation.

03:16.260 --> 03:17.320
It's just speculation.

03:19.280 --> 03:20.960
So what kind of person

03:21.660 --> 03:22.670
do you think this college girl

03:22.670 --> 03:23.470
could have fallen in love with?

03:24.780 --> 03:25.970
There are many possibilities.

03:26.750 --> 03:27.430
A senior,

03:27.510 --> 03:28.440
an elder brother,

03:28.579 --> 03:29.600
or a teacher.

03:31.670 --> 03:32.590
All possible.

03:39.440 --> 03:41.490
Who could be the one that sent the anonymous letter

03:41.630 --> 03:42.910
about Deng Man?

03:44.040 --> 03:46.550
If the police received the anonymous letter,

03:46.750 --> 03:48.350
they would definitely contact the school.

03:48.829 --> 03:49.310
Right.

03:49.550 --> 03:50.430
Ask the school.

03:55.190 --> 03:55.910
Director Gao.

03:56.190 --> 03:57.670
I want to ask you something about Deng Man.

03:58.710 --> 03:59.610
Deng Man?

04:00.030 --> 04:02.070
The girl who committed suicide by jumping into the lake?

04:02.550 --> 04:03.470
Yes.

04:03.590 --> 04:04.470
Director Gao.

04:04.710 --> 04:05.870
I want to ask.

04:05.910 --> 04:06.910
There was an anonymous letter

04:06.930 --> 04:08.670
about Deng Man.

04:08.910 --> 04:10.390
Do you know about this?

04:10.910 --> 04:11.430
Yes.

04:12.120 --> 04:14.490
What did the anonymous letter say?

04:14.870 --> 04:16.950
That Deng Man didn't commit suicide,

04:17.040 --> 04:18.610
and she was murdered.

04:18.790 --> 04:20.769
It requested the police to reopen the investigation.

04:20.940 --> 04:22.070
Thank you, Director Gao.

04:23.100 --> 04:25.900
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

04:50.130 --> 04:54.070
[Quiet Vine]

04:54.110 --> 04:55.710
"Hiroshima Mon Amour."

05:00.490 --> 05:00.860
[I'll teach you some cute word art.]

05:00.490 --> 05:00.860
[I understand how it works, but where do I get a pair of hands like yours?]

05:00.890 --> 05:01.540
[Please don't...]

05:02.080 --> 05:02.760
[Seasons change, and there're always new stories worth looking forward to.]

05:05.150 --> 05:06.090
[It's panda!]

05:06.710 --> 05:07.310
[Following]

05:07.310 --> 05:09.120
[Following 103 accounts, distributed in 9 areas of interest]

05:18.310 --> 05:19.350
Did Man

05:18.610 --> 05:19.360
[Quiet Vine
Waiting for you]

05:19.470 --> 05:21.030
really have other friends?

05:20.250 --> 05:24.260
[Quiet Vine]

05:22.470 --> 05:23.310
How could this person

05:23.330 --> 05:24.570
have left no trace at all?

05:27.200 --> 05:29.840
[Quiet Vine]

05:40.090 --> 05:43.040
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

05:47.900 --> 05:49.380
This is the watch Man usually wore.

05:50.430 --> 05:51.390
Could this be

05:52.070 --> 05:53.830
Man's alt account on Weibo?

05:52.550 --> 05:53.030
[Waiting for you]

05:53.990 --> 05:56.520
[So sweet]

05:57.630 --> 05:58.310
I didn't expect

05:58.350 --> 05:59.550
Man's feelings for Jiang Chengyi

05:59.550 --> 06:00.430
were so obvious.

06:01.470 --> 06:02.550
So,

06:02.990 --> 06:05.470
what Coach Zhou said is true.

06:03.970 --> 06:05.520
[Would it be better if I died...]

06:05.520 --> 06:08.640
[Please, stop pushing me. I can't do it, I really can't!]

06:09.700 --> 06:10.370
[Please, stop pushing me. I can't do it, I really can't!]

06:10.370 --> 06:15.440
[Why can't you let me go?]

06:10.370 --> 06:15.440
[I wash your jerseys and clean your shoes. I am willing to be your slave.]

06:16.730 --> 06:18.610
[I don't want to see her again.]

06:16.730 --> 06:18.610
[My favorite volleyball class has become my nightmare.]

06:18.610 --> 06:20.920
[Oh no, why am I so stupid! I should have hidden it better!]

06:21.390 --> 06:22.950
The laundry.

06:24.000 --> 06:25.790
Volleyball class.

06:34.310 --> 06:35.840
Man.

06:36.230 --> 06:36.840
You're back.

06:36.860 --> 06:37.690
Are you doing the laundry?

06:38.270 --> 06:39.520
Let me help you. That's a lot.

06:39.550 --> 06:41.210
No need. I can wash them myself.

06:44.020 --> 06:45.070
[Ding Jing]

06:45.670 --> 06:46.350
Ding Jing?

06:50.320 --> 06:52.070
We are both in the volleyball team,

06:52.110 --> 06:54.400
so I thought I'd help her wash hers.

06:55.060 --> 06:56.360
She didn't bully you, did she?

06:57.270 --> 06:57.790
No.

06:57.860 --> 06:59.730
How could it be? She wouldn't dare.

07:00.590 --> 07:01.790
I have a package.

07:01.830 --> 07:03.190
Go to the first floor and get it for me.

07:03.340 --> 07:04.150
Go ahead.

07:06.510 --> 07:08.130
Did Ding Jing really drop out of school?

07:06.740 --> 07:09.300
[Baggage Deposit]

07:09.720 --> 07:10.510
Yes.

07:09.920 --> 07:11.210
[Ninghai University]

07:11.270 --> 07:12.670
She suddenly left a few days ago.

07:12.830 --> 07:14.480
She didn't even pack her things in the dorm.

07:15.070 --> 07:16.430
When I contacted her,

07:16.790 --> 07:17.790
she said

07:17.910 --> 07:19.390
she had already arrived in the US.

07:19.430 --> 07:21.060
But she's been in college for two years.

07:21.190 --> 07:22.030
Dropping out just like that?

07:22.230 --> 07:23.190
Isn't that

07:23.230 --> 07:24.070
two years wasted in vain?

07:24.820 --> 07:25.950
Who knows?

07:26.750 --> 07:27.630
I guess she's just rich

07:27.660 --> 07:28.580
and willful.

07:39.880 --> 07:40.770
Ding Jing.

07:55.760 --> 07:56.460
Ding Jing.

07:59.190 --> 08:00.670
Get up. Look what time it is.

08:00.990 --> 08:02.270
You're so annoying.

08:02.310 --> 08:03.860
You won't even let me sleep.

08:04.130 --> 08:05.440
You don't sleep at night or get up during the day.

08:05.470 --> 08:06.510
How inappropriate.

08:06.530 --> 08:07.120
Hurry up.

08:15.550 --> 08:16.470
I really can't

08:16.470 --> 08:17.980
live with you anymore.

08:26.390 --> 08:27.750
I know what you did.

08:41.429 --> 08:42.140
Ding Jing.

08:42.600 --> 08:43.890
How many times have I told you

08:43.950 --> 08:45.270
not to look at your phone

08:45.350 --> 08:46.020
on stairs?

08:46.790 --> 08:48.200
How many times have I told you

08:48.230 --> 08:49.740
to stop nagging me?

08:49.830 --> 08:50.790
Arrange your clothes.

08:51.270 --> 08:51.870
You're a girl.

08:51.890 --> 08:52.810
How indecent.

08:53.110 --> 08:54.380
What's wrong with my clothes?

08:55.020 --> 08:56.510
All you know is nagging me.

08:56.750 --> 08:58.040
If you have so much time, why don't you discipline my dad

08:58.070 --> 08:59.340
and see what he's doing outside?

08:59.510 --> 09:00.190
Come down for breakfast.

09:01.990 --> 09:02.790
So annoying.

09:05.350 --> 09:06.830
Endless nagging.

09:12.990 --> 09:13.790
Sit down and eat.

09:14.350 --> 09:14.830
I'll pass.

09:14.950 --> 09:15.740
I'm on a diet.

09:16.380 --> 09:17.280
It's a 16-hour plus 8-hour diet,

09:17.310 --> 09:18.790
so sleeping until two o'clock is perfect.

09:18.790 --> 09:19.830
Why did you have to wake me up?

09:21.790 --> 09:22.400
Ding Jing.

09:23.370 --> 09:24.360
Didn't you always say

09:24.390 --> 09:25.230
you wanted to move out?

09:25.420 --> 09:26.600
You can leave right now.

09:26.670 --> 09:27.720
I'm waiting for my dad to come back

09:27.750 --> 09:28.780
so I can ask him for money.

09:28.870 --> 09:29.390
I want to see

09:29.430 --> 09:30.620
where he spent all his money.

09:32.900 --> 09:34.740
We're having dinner with Jiang Chengyi's parents this weekend.

09:34.870 --> 09:35.430
Don't give my dad dirty looks

09:35.470 --> 09:36.390
during dinner.

09:38.630 --> 09:40.290
What is this? So ugly.

09:54.600 --> 09:56.800
[To Ding Jing]

09:59.840 --> 10:02.120
[To Ding Jing]

10:34.750 --> 10:35.770
No problem.

10:36.190 --> 10:37.650
Then leave this one to me.

10:37.670 --> 10:38.540
I'll take it.

10:39.860 --> 10:40.790
Not today.

10:40.870 --> 10:42.160
I don't have enough time today.

10:42.180 --> 10:43.000
How about tomorrow?

10:43.160 --> 10:44.210
I'll go see you tomorrow.

10:45.750 --> 10:46.480
Sure.

11:13.480 --> 11:14.500
I know what you did

11:14.500 --> 11:15.360
to Deng Man.

11:23.020 --> 11:24.010
Close the door.

11:25.360 --> 11:26.730
I said, close the door.

11:32.500 --> 11:33.680
Let me show you something.

11:37.880 --> 11:40.020
Why do you have this video?

11:40.110 --> 11:42.050
Stay away from me.

11:44.570 --> 11:45.980
Making so much noise.

11:46.460 --> 11:48.080
Aren't you worried the whole school will know about this?

11:57.510 --> 11:58.280
Miss.

11:59.730 --> 12:00.830
10 yuan for parking.

12:00.900 --> 12:02.180
You scared me!

12:14.150 --> 12:15.280
Jing.

12:15.690 --> 12:17.250
Did you crawl here? Why so slow?

12:19.100 --> 12:20.020
Dear princess.

12:20.050 --> 12:21.290
I'm not like you, okay?

12:21.540 --> 12:23.170
I have to work.

12:23.390 --> 12:24.470
I had to sneak out

12:24.510 --> 12:25.910
in advance to be here.

12:27.880 --> 12:28.650
What's wrong?

12:28.870 --> 12:30.590
Are you in a bad mood?

12:31.030 --> 12:32.360
Someone followed me

12:33.770 --> 12:35.210
and sent me an anonymous letter

12:35.310 --> 12:36.190
to threaten me.

12:38.850 --> 12:39.770
Someone followed you?

12:39.940 --> 12:41.280
Who was it?

12:41.310 --> 12:42.490
Did you call the police?

12:42.520 --> 12:43.850
Enough! You're so annoying.

12:43.880 --> 12:45.120
How would I know who it was?

12:50.150 --> 12:51.470
I called you here today

12:51.540 --> 12:53.140
to ask you for a favor.

12:53.880 --> 12:55.180
Help me contact Wang Qiang

12:55.630 --> 12:56.590
and ask him for something.

12:59.080 --> 13:00.270
What is it?

13:01.920 --> 13:03.300
Pepper spray,

13:04.540 --> 13:05.740
an alarm,

13:07.140 --> 13:07.790
or a taser.

13:09.480 --> 13:10.430
A stun gun would work too.

13:13.400 --> 13:14.460
A stun gun?

13:16.560 --> 13:17.980
But it's illegal.

13:19.710 --> 13:21.120
Wang Qiang can get it.

13:21.390 --> 13:22.870
All you need to do is go find him.

13:23.590 --> 13:24.600
Also, help me ask him

13:24.630 --> 13:26.350
how the thing I asked him to do is going.

13:28.070 --> 13:28.910
Jing.

13:30.480 --> 13:31.620
How about you

13:32.510 --> 13:34.350
contact him directly in the future?

13:35.270 --> 13:37.140
I'm worried it might be

13:37.870 --> 13:39.350
inconvenient sometimes if you keep contacting him through me.

13:44.360 --> 13:45.190
Jing.

13:45.280 --> 13:46.200
Don't get me wrong.

13:46.220 --> 13:47.530
That's not what I meant.

13:47.860 --> 13:49.300
I mean,

13:49.320 --> 13:50.100
I don't know very well

13:50.130 --> 13:51.540
about what's going on between you two.

13:51.720 --> 13:52.420
Sometimes,

13:52.470 --> 13:53.790
the message you convey to me

13:53.870 --> 13:55.030
is just a few words.

13:55.120 --> 13:57.230
I... I'm worried if I can't explain it clearly,

13:57.600 --> 13:58.980
I'll waste your time.

14:00.890 --> 14:03.080
You're worried you'd waste your own time, right?

14:09.650 --> 14:10.670
Liu Yujie.

14:11.180 --> 14:13.140
I think I need to remind you.

14:13.660 --> 14:14.570
Your dad,

14:15.550 --> 14:16.420
your mom,

14:17.040 --> 14:17.980
and you.

14:19.270 --> 14:21.550
I'm providing for your whole family.

14:22.850 --> 14:24.320
Without me,

14:25.040 --> 14:26.000
your family would have gone bankrupt

14:26.030 --> 14:27.230
10,000 times, okay?

14:42.150 --> 14:43.010
Jing.

14:43.270 --> 14:44.340
I'm sorry.

14:44.470 --> 14:45.980
I was rude just now.

14:46.100 --> 14:47.900
Please don't be angry, Jing.

14:49.100 --> 14:49.930
Remember,

14:51.350 --> 14:52.440
just do

14:52.470 --> 14:53.390
as I say.

14:55.290 --> 14:56.610
Contact Wang Qiang

14:56.860 --> 14:58.770
and get me the thing and the photos I want as soon as possible.

14:59.650 --> 15:00.390
You know

15:01.500 --> 15:02.580
how impatient I am.

15:05.120 --> 15:06.000
I know.

15:09.640 --> 15:11.050
Jing, where are you going?

15:58.250 --> 15:59.910
Liu Yujie...

16:05.630 --> 16:06.810
Are you following me?

16:06.870 --> 16:08.760
So it's you who's been following me!

16:09.470 --> 16:10.990
I wondered who put it there.

16:11.030 --> 16:12.080
It was you, wasn't it?

16:12.110 --> 16:12.950
I don't even know what you're talking about!

16:12.990 --> 16:13.590
You don't know?

16:13.610 --> 16:14.910
Don't you know what this is?

16:15.020 --> 16:16.560
I don't know.

16:16.740 --> 16:17.480
You don't know?

16:17.510 --> 16:18.990
Only you know things about me.

16:19.060 --> 16:19.680
You don't know?

16:19.710 --> 16:20.360
It wasn't me!

16:20.390 --> 16:22.230
Jing, let go of me!

16:22.230 --> 16:23.550
Only you know I'd be here.

16:23.620 --> 16:24.530
Excuse me, Miss.

16:24.790 --> 16:25.120
Please...

16:25.150 --> 16:25.860
Please do not disturb

16:25.890 --> 16:26.870
other customers' dining.

16:27.180 --> 16:27.800
Surveillance camera.

16:27.820 --> 16:28.590
Show me the surveillance footage.

16:28.660 --> 16:29.610
I want to see the surveillance footage.

16:29.640 --> 16:30.500
-As for the surveillance footage,
-Let go of me!

16:30.550 --> 16:31.730
only the police can check it.

16:31.790 --> 16:32.410
I'm sorry.

16:32.470 --> 16:33.870
No. I have to check it today!

16:33.910 --> 16:35.250
I lost something here!

16:35.730 --> 16:36.500
If you keep doing this,

16:36.520 --> 16:37.570
I'll have to call the police.

16:38.770 --> 16:39.610
Let go!

16:42.620 --> 16:43.480
What are you looking at?

16:43.500 --> 16:44.230
Move!

16:45.020 --> 16:45.790
Sorry about that.

16:45.810 --> 16:46.690
Sorry.

16:46.870 --> 16:47.720
Sorry.

16:47.930 --> 16:49.080
What's wrong with you!

16:49.520 --> 16:50.750
Sorry about that. Sorry.

17:18.680 --> 17:19.720
You're stalking me, huh?

17:20.000 --> 17:21.260
You want to mess with me?

17:21.750 --> 17:22.960
Aren't you worried

17:22.990 --> 17:24.349
I'd expose all the things you did back then?

17:27.900 --> 17:28.780
It wasn't you?

17:28.860 --> 17:30.280
Who else could it be?

17:30.350 --> 17:30.960
Is there a third person

17:30.990 --> 17:32.360
who knows about this?

17:32.630 --> 17:34.020
Then go ahead and investigate.

17:34.150 --> 17:35.470
Go find out who's playing these tricks

17:35.510 --> 17:36.730
behind my back.

17:36.830 --> 17:38.040
Anyway, I'm telling you,

17:38.450 --> 17:39.470
if this kind of thing

17:39.510 --> 17:40.500
happens again,

17:40.610 --> 17:41.680
I'll expose

17:41.710 --> 17:42.630
all those things you've done!

17:43.320 --> 17:44.760
I'll drag you to hell with me!

17:47.930 --> 17:49.550
What the hell is this!

17:55.530 --> 17:56.830
If it wasn't her,

17:57.550 --> 17:58.670
who else could it be?

18:03.260 --> 18:04.230
Could it be...

18:07.580 --> 18:11.110
[Public Security]

18:11.030 --> 18:12.320
According to the clues we found,

18:12.350 --> 18:13.310
we've compared

18:13.590 --> 18:14.930
the information of

18:15.030 --> 18:16.200
all women aged 18 to 35

18:16.230 --> 18:17.790
with a medical background

18:17.790 --> 18:18.550
in this city.

18:19.140 --> 18:20.110
We've ruled out

18:20.140 --> 18:20.840
the possibility of the murderer

18:20.870 --> 18:22.160
having a medical background.

18:26.090 --> 18:26.790
Yiming.

18:27.200 --> 18:27.870
How's it going on your side?

18:27.990 --> 18:28.590
Not very well.

18:28.610 --> 18:29.640
The portraits have been distributed

18:29.670 --> 18:30.430
to the local police stations.

18:30.540 --> 18:31.280
But according to the feedback,

18:31.300 --> 18:32.680
there were only few valuable clues.

18:32.810 --> 18:33.550
I just contacted

18:33.550 --> 18:34.230
the traffic police battalion, too.

18:34.350 --> 18:34.870
They said

18:34.890 --> 18:35.760
they've never seen this person.

18:38.070 --> 18:39.350
She disappeared just like that?

18:39.430 --> 18:40.400
That seems impossible.

18:42.830 --> 18:43.560
It's okay.

18:43.750 --> 18:45.760
Notify all departments

18:45.790 --> 18:46.710
and ask them to keep watching.

18:46.830 --> 18:47.540
She won't be able to escape.

18:47.810 --> 18:48.350
Okay.

18:48.350 --> 18:48.750
Got it.

18:50.030 --> 18:50.550
Hao.

18:50.570 --> 18:51.790
What tea is this?

18:52.740 --> 18:53.550
It's not even as good as my plain water.

18:53.590 --> 18:54.270
You don't understand.

19:28.210 --> 19:30.760
[Lu Yan]

20:53.290 --> 20:58.560
[Lu Yan] [Log in]

20:58.840 --> 20:59.530
[Founder of Boya Porcelain]

21:01.800 --> 21:07.800
[Founder of Boya Porcelain]

21:12.510 --> 21:13.350
Qianqian.

21:13.960 --> 21:14.830
Man.

21:15.420 --> 21:16.390
Rest assured.

21:17.260 --> 21:18.910
I'll definitely get to the bottom of it.

21:29.620 --> 21:30.150
Come in.

21:31.710 --> 21:32.450
Mr. Wen.

21:32.830 --> 21:35.170
Here are the project proposals sent to us recently.

21:35.450 --> 21:37.000
I've screened them.

21:37.030 --> 21:38.590
These are the relatively good ones.

21:39.830 --> 21:40.230
Okay.

21:41.750 --> 21:43.590
Are there any medical-themed projects?

21:45.570 --> 21:46.570
There is one,

21:47.140 --> 21:48.080
but

21:48.310 --> 21:49.190
I screened it out.

21:49.190 --> 21:49.630
It was

21:49.670 --> 21:51.150
a small, unknown company

21:51.290 --> 21:53.460
which wanted to make a B-rated online drama.

21:53.560 --> 21:54.270
The point is,

21:54.550 --> 21:55.330
they can't possibly afford

21:55.360 --> 21:56.520
the artists of our company.

21:56.750 --> 21:57.590
Contact them

21:57.820 --> 21:58.930
and tell them I want to invest.

21:59.140 --> 22:00.230
But the condition is

22:01.030 --> 22:01.870
I'll be in charge.

22:05.020 --> 22:05.920
Is there a problem?

22:06.120 --> 22:06.640
No.

22:06.750 --> 22:07.270
No, no.

22:07.790 --> 22:09.340
I'll contact them right away.

22:23.790 --> 22:24.510
Peng.

22:24.550 --> 22:25.430
Are you up?

22:25.550 --> 22:26.600
I saw the news.

22:26.670 --> 22:28.100
There's a snowstorm in New York.

22:28.190 --> 22:29.950
Remember to keep warm

22:30.070 --> 22:31.270
and wear more clothes.

22:31.470 --> 22:33.380
Be careful when you go out.

22:34.380 --> 22:35.700
[Copy] [Delete]

22:35.840 --> 22:37.380
[Cancel] [Delete]

22:35.840 --> 22:37.380
[Confirm Delete]

22:48.870 --> 22:51.890
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

22:56.990 --> 22:58.080
Morning, Mr. Wang.

22:58.990 --> 22:59.970
Morning, Dr. Lu.

23:27.170 --> 23:27.780
[Please close and lock the door]

23:27.290 --> 23:28.260
Come on.

23:28.280 --> 23:29.510
I'm scheduling surgeries.

23:37.330 --> 23:37.940
Lu Yan.

23:37.970 --> 23:39.230
What are you waiting for?

23:39.260 --> 23:40.240
Come on, we're having a meeting.

23:40.320 --> 23:41.460
You dare to be late for Director Sun's morning meeting?

23:41.490 --> 23:42.450
Aren't you worried you'll get scolded?

23:43.300 --> 23:44.310
You're smearing me again.

23:44.540 --> 23:45.790
When did I ever scold you?

23:46.300 --> 23:47.790
Last time was when I got off work yesterday.

23:48.360 --> 23:50.080
Then you must deserve it.

23:50.550 --> 23:51.680
You're right, Matron Qiao.

23:51.710 --> 23:52.630
It was all my fault.

23:52.760 --> 23:53.200
I'll correct it.

23:53.220 --> 23:53.950
I will.

23:54.340 --> 23:54.900
Alright, alright.

23:54.940 --> 23:56.460
Let's continue.

23:57.390 --> 23:59.170
You'll take care of

23:59.200 --> 24:00.540
the spinal surgeries

24:00.860 --> 24:01.560
and gynecological surgeries in the morning.

24:01.640 --> 24:01.920
Okay.

24:01.960 --> 24:02.990
Li and Qingqing,

24:03.070 --> 24:04.150
you two will be in charge of the surgeries of General Surgery

24:04.170 --> 24:05.160
and Obstetrics and Gynecology Department.

24:05.390 --> 24:07.440
And there's a

24:07.470 --> 24:08.580
hernia surgery at short notice.

24:09.500 --> 24:10.180
Lu Yan.

24:10.320 --> 24:10.970
What do you think?

24:11.270 --> 24:12.020
I'll leave it to you, alright?

24:14.440 --> 24:15.290
No problem.

24:17.740 --> 24:18.710
Listen. You see...

24:18.710 --> 24:19.270
Coffee.

24:20.770 --> 24:21.870
The patient

24:21.890 --> 24:22.580
of spinal surgery

24:22.680 --> 24:24.090
has a history of hypertension.

24:24.190 --> 24:25.620
During intraoperative drug delivery,

24:25.670 --> 24:26.240
pay attention to

24:26.270 --> 24:27.030
the blood pressure changes.

24:27.110 --> 24:27.600
Okay.

24:30.270 --> 24:31.040
Yan.

24:31.710 --> 24:32.600
Your surgery just now

24:32.640 --> 24:33.350
was amazing.

24:33.660 --> 24:34.190
When can I

24:34.190 --> 24:35.480
become as good as you?

24:35.910 --> 24:37.220
It's a process.

24:40.630 --> 24:42.190
According to the patient's condition,

24:42.220 --> 24:43.630
I suggest general anesthesia.

24:43.710 --> 24:45.170
So please rest assured.

24:45.360 --> 24:47.910
We are very confident.

26:25.750 --> 26:26.290
Yes.

26:26.330 --> 26:28.330
The patient needs a coronary stent.

26:28.570 --> 26:30.180
He's afraid of pain and wants general anesthesia.

26:30.210 --> 26:31.400
But I think local anesthesia will suffice.

26:31.430 --> 26:32.540
After all, it's a minimally invasive surgery.

26:33.350 --> 26:34.980
I'll talk to him again.

26:35.470 --> 26:36.000
Okay.

26:36.030 --> 26:36.640
That's all.

26:43.480 --> 26:44.240
Yan.

26:45.750 --> 26:46.600
Yan.

26:46.920 --> 26:48.930
Do you think I should put it up here,

26:48.960 --> 26:50.010
here,

26:50.030 --> 26:51.140
or here?

26:52.680 --> 26:54.700
But if I put up pictures so randomly like this,

26:54.790 --> 26:55.850
do you think Matron Qiao

26:55.870 --> 26:57.130
will criticize me?

26:57.150 --> 26:58.440
As long as you're happy,

26:58.480 --> 26:59.870
just put it up wherever you want.

26:59.900 --> 27:01.810
If Matron Qiao criticizes you,

27:01.840 --> 27:02.700
I'll have your back.

27:02.730 --> 27:03.310
Okay.

27:03.330 --> 27:04.210
I'll put up

27:04.270 --> 27:05.470
a photo of us too.

27:05.910 --> 27:06.760
I'll put it here.

27:07.880 --> 27:08.770
Let me ask you.

27:08.980 --> 27:10.120
Do you love me more,

27:10.150 --> 27:11.420
or your prince charming more?

27:13.430 --> 27:14.450
You are like my palm,

27:14.470 --> 27:15.630
and he's like the back of my hand.

27:15.660 --> 27:17.260
Both of you are important to me.

27:17.430 --> 27:19.300
Where did you learn these terms?

27:19.320 --> 27:19.960
No.

27:19.980 --> 27:20.800
You must love me more.

27:20.830 --> 27:21.870
Of course.

27:56.640 --> 27:58.090
Dr. Lu, are you off work?

28:01.200 --> 28:01.970
Lu Yan.

28:02.000 --> 28:05.280
[Outpatient]

28:03.940 --> 28:04.620
Senior.

28:05.850 --> 28:06.930
Why are you getting off work so late?

28:07.790 --> 28:08.920
It's my first day here.

28:08.950 --> 28:10.280
There was a lot of work

28:10.310 --> 28:10.840
that needed to be done.

28:10.870 --> 28:11.400
I just finished.

28:11.710 --> 28:12.580
You...

28:12.660 --> 28:13.710
Why are you here?

28:14.720 --> 28:16.030
I'm here to ask you for a favor.

28:17.460 --> 28:20.690
I invested in a medical-themed online drama.

28:20.590 --> 28:21.450
[Living]

28:21.340 --> 28:23.070
The heroine is an anesthesiologist.

28:23.310 --> 28:24.000
So,

28:24.350 --> 28:25.810
I want you to be my consultant.

28:27.230 --> 28:28.020
Sure.

28:29.500 --> 28:31.040
If you're not in a hurry,

28:31.070 --> 28:32.140
I'll check it for you later.

28:33.770 --> 28:35.030
Luckily, you agreed.

28:35.110 --> 28:36.280
Otherwise, I wouldn't know

28:36.310 --> 28:37.180
who to ask for help.

28:38.120 --> 28:39.260
You studied medicine too.

28:39.280 --> 28:39.940
Why did you return all the knowledge you've learned

28:40.030 --> 28:41.190
to Dr. Han?

28:41.880 --> 28:43.490
I didn't tell him that I came this time.

28:43.680 --> 28:45.790
And I'm worried he'll say

28:45.870 --> 28:46.670
I'm wasting his beloved pupil,

28:46.700 --> 28:48.380
Dr. Lu's precious time.

28:48.400 --> 28:50.000
He'll blame me when I come next time.

28:50.620 --> 28:52.200
I have something to do later.

28:52.220 --> 28:53.230
I have to go.

28:54.070 --> 28:54.870
I drove here.

28:54.910 --> 28:55.470
How about

28:55.490 --> 28:56.250
I give you a ride?

28:58.780 --> 28:59.490
No need.

28:59.780 --> 29:01.060
I can go by myself.

29:01.150 --> 29:02.140
Let me give you a ride.

29:02.350 --> 29:03.820
It's quite late. I'm worried.

29:03.870 --> 29:04.950
Don't worry.

29:05.030 --> 29:06.150
I've had a new start.

29:06.500 --> 29:07.510
I'll check it for you later.

29:07.830 --> 29:08.450
I'm off.

29:08.630 --> 29:09.270
Bye.

29:09.580 --> 29:10.860
Be careful.

29:23.430 --> 29:25.000
Uncles. I invited you here today

29:25.030 --> 29:26.180
to thank you

29:26.210 --> 29:27.430
for taking care of me these days.

29:27.470 --> 29:28.960
This toast is to all of you.

29:29.080 --> 29:30.700
Alright. Come on.

29:34.150 --> 29:35.130
Jing.

29:35.510 --> 29:36.170
You can really hold your liquor.

29:37.030 --> 29:37.940
You must have taken it

29:38.030 --> 29:39.020
after your father.

29:39.050 --> 29:40.760
Maybe I'm even better than him.

29:41.230 --> 29:42.080
Jing.

29:42.110 --> 29:43.420
You're too kind.

29:43.450 --> 29:44.090
We are

29:44.110 --> 29:45.580
your father's friends, after all.

29:45.720 --> 29:47.030
Don't say that.

29:47.080 --> 29:48.380
We are different.

29:48.640 --> 29:49.430
So you wouldn't do business with me

29:49.470 --> 29:50.740
if it weren't for my dad?

29:51.550 --> 29:52.780
That's nonsense.

29:52.960 --> 29:53.880
Your porcelain

29:53.950 --> 29:54.750
is of such high quality.

29:54.850 --> 29:56.280
It’s really worth collecting.

29:56.340 --> 29:57.810
Han, am I right?

29:57.950 --> 29:58.630
Yes.

29:58.660 --> 30:00.190
It's really worth collecting.

30:00.570 --> 30:01.330
Jing.

30:01.430 --> 30:03.200
We should communicate more in the future.

30:03.230 --> 30:03.970
Sure.

30:04.190 --> 30:05.030
Come on.

30:05.190 --> 30:06.850
Let's propose a toast to Jing together.

30:06.870 --> 30:07.440
Alright. Alright.

30:07.460 --> 30:07.710
Come on.

30:07.870 --> 30:08.150
Come on.

30:08.190 --> 30:08.590
You're too kind.

30:08.700 --> 30:09.340
A toast to you.

30:11.100 --> 30:11.900
Pour me wine.

30:11.950 --> 30:13.830
This is really great.

30:14.590 --> 30:15.640
I forgot.

30:15.870 --> 30:16.640
Yeah.

30:17.390 --> 30:17.750
Come on, Jing.

30:17.790 --> 30:18.030
Come on.

30:18.090 --> 30:18.960
-Be my guest.
-Come on, Jing.

30:19.020 --> 30:19.580
Come on.

30:22.230 --> 30:23.410
You can really hold your liquor, Jing.

30:23.590 --> 30:24.340
Good for you.

30:24.370 --> 30:25.480
I specially prepared some gifts

30:25.510 --> 30:26.420
for you today.

30:26.470 --> 30:27.030
I thought you could bring them back

30:27.050 --> 30:27.850
to your families.

30:27.910 --> 30:28.790
You're too kind.

30:29.250 --> 30:29.910
It's nothing.

30:29.910 --> 30:30.430
You're too kind.

30:30.470 --> 30:31.150
It's nothing.

30:31.350 --> 30:32.100
It's not necessary.

30:32.380 --> 30:34.220
We should keep the goodies within the group, right?

30:35.270 --> 30:36.020
Seriously.

30:36.050 --> 30:37.030
Thank you. Thank you.

30:37.030 --> 30:37.730
Be careful.

30:37.970 --> 30:38.780
Thank you.

30:38.870 --> 30:40.090
Uncle Huang, take a look.

30:40.220 --> 30:41.780
Such a big gift.

30:41.830 --> 30:43.290
Uncle Han, this is yours.

30:43.670 --> 30:44.990
I picked all these

30:45.070 --> 30:46.310
myself.

30:46.330 --> 30:46.830
Really?

30:46.830 --> 30:47.430
That's really nice of you.

30:47.450 --> 30:48.110
So nice.

30:48.110 --> 30:48.930
Let me take a look.

30:49.050 --> 30:50.160
Let me see my gift.

30:50.430 --> 30:51.710
The quality of these porcelains

30:51.790 --> 30:52.820
are really great.

30:53.550 --> 30:54.290
So nice of you.

30:54.310 --> 30:55.630
Good stuff. Good stuff.

30:56.170 --> 30:57.560
Nice quality.

30:57.950 --> 30:59.400
See? It's done just like that.

30:59.650 --> 31:00.630
I'm sure you'll make it.

31:00.650 --> 31:01.910
You have great taste.

31:02.110 --> 31:03.410
These old men.

31:04.830 --> 31:05.480
This...

31:05.790 --> 31:06.990
What's written on this?

31:07.660 --> 31:08.750
Ding Jing.

31:08.960 --> 31:11.580
What exactly did you do

31:11.920 --> 31:13.310
to Deng Man?

31:14.150 --> 31:15.190
You'll die a horrible death?

31:15.210 --> 31:17.340
You killed Deng Man, right?

31:19.190 --> 31:19.740
Jing.

31:20.730 --> 31:21.510
What's this about?

31:21.530 --> 31:22.260
Jing.

31:22.460 --> 31:23.280
What's this about?

31:23.510 --> 31:25.150
[Ding Jing, what exactly did you do to Deng Man?
You killed Deng Man, right?]

31:26.310 --> 31:27.110
It's written like this

31:27.110 --> 31:28.150
on all their cards.

31:30.640 --> 31:31.370
It wasn't me.

31:38.540 --> 31:39.270
Jing.

31:39.320 --> 31:40.090
What should we do?

31:40.110 --> 31:41.780
What's going on, Jing?

31:44.310 --> 31:44.870
Ding Jing.

31:44.960 --> 31:46.740
You have only one choice now.

31:47.070 --> 31:48.200
Admit on Weibo

31:48.230 --> 31:49.880
what you did to Deng Man back then.

31:50.030 --> 31:51.030
Otherwise, you'll suffer the consequences.

31:51.070 --> 31:51.830
Jing.

31:52.110 --> 31:53.040
A-Are we

31:53.070 --> 31:54.070
being followed, Jing?

31:54.110 --> 31:55.110
Should we call the police?

31:55.200 --> 31:55.870
Jing.

31:55.890 --> 31:57.430
Jing, what should we do now?

31:57.650 --> 31:59.200
What are you thinking!

32:02.250 --> 32:03.000
Jing.

32:32.840 --> 32:33.550
Wait.

32:43.000 --> 32:43.650
Lu Yan?

32:47.310 --> 32:49.010
Why are you

32:49.420 --> 32:50.470
dressed like this?

32:54.820 --> 32:56.020
I just...

32:59.810 --> 33:00.740
Have something to do.

33:04.750 --> 33:05.980
Why are you here?

33:06.700 --> 33:07.580
To see me?

33:10.250 --> 33:10.890
Yes.

33:10.910 --> 33:11.690
Because

33:12.120 --> 33:13.830
you haven't replied to my WeChat messages the past couple of days.

33:14.450 --> 33:15.750
I was a little worried,

33:15.780 --> 33:16.780
so I came to check on you.

33:17.390 --> 33:18.150
I...

33:18.230 --> 33:19.790
There's no need to worry about me.

33:21.030 --> 33:21.710
It's just

33:22.270 --> 33:23.990
I've been busy lately.

33:27.050 --> 33:28.870
Have you been working overtime at the hospital?

33:36.280 --> 33:37.420
I'm off.

33:41.030 --> 33:41.860
Lu Yan!

33:42.240 --> 33:42.980
Lu Yan.

33:49.470 --> 33:50.150
Lu Yan.

33:50.930 --> 33:52.060
I know

33:53.010 --> 33:54.880
you don't want to see me now.

33:57.270 --> 33:58.590
We don't have to meet.

33:59.400 --> 34:00.950
But please,

34:01.400 --> 34:02.550
at least reply to my messages,

34:02.780 --> 34:03.380
okay?

34:04.940 --> 34:05.520
I...

34:06.280 --> 34:07.250
Okay.

35:09.420 --> 35:14.950
[Huiting Complex]

35:09.830 --> 35:10.580
Morning, Lu.

35:10.630 --> 35:11.070
Morning.

35:14.850 --> 35:16.050
Why are you here?

35:16.390 --> 35:18.040
I want to know if you're free today.

35:18.880 --> 35:20.000
What's the matter?

35:21.030 --> 35:21.870
That medical drama I'm working on

35:21.900 --> 35:22.900
is a bit tight in schedule.

35:22.920 --> 35:24.590
The scriptwriter wants you to be his consultant.

35:26.440 --> 35:27.840
I remember

35:28.040 --> 35:29.910
I have no surgery this afternoon.

35:30.140 --> 35:31.860
I think I can get off work on time.

35:32.350 --> 35:33.160
That's great.

35:33.260 --> 35:35.140
Text me after work.

35:35.230 --> 35:35.910
I'll come pick you up.

35:37.000 --> 35:37.710
It's no trouble at all.

35:37.750 --> 35:39.310
Don't make it so grand.

35:39.330 --> 35:40.610
I can go by myself.

35:40.730 --> 35:42.100
I invited you to be my consultant.

35:42.150 --> 35:43.850
Of course I have to show you my respect.

35:43.870 --> 35:44.780
In the future,

35:44.800 --> 35:47.670
I'll count on you on this project, Dr. Lu.

35:48.240 --> 35:49.970
Don't mention it.

35:50.030 --> 35:50.570
I'm leaving.

35:51.350 --> 35:52.050
Let me give you a ride.

35:52.550 --> 35:53.220
No need.

35:53.240 --> 35:54.250
There's a traffic jam at this hour.

35:54.340 --> 35:55.540
Riding a bike is faster.

35:59.000 --> 35:59.700
Take the breakfast then.

36:00.230 --> 36:01.280
Eat it at the hospital.

36:01.550 --> 36:03.100
Okay, I'm leaving.

36:03.350 --> 36:04.010
Bye.

36:16.550 --> 36:18.540
[Huiting Complex]

36:28.570 --> 36:30.070
After reading the whole script,

36:30.110 --> 36:31.800
I suggest

36:31.820 --> 36:32.440
you change

36:32.470 --> 36:33.990
the title "anesthetist" throughout the whole script

36:34.010 --> 36:35.750
to "anesthesiologist".

36:35.910 --> 36:37.380
Because we anesthesiologists

36:37.470 --> 36:38.370
are the same as

36:38.470 --> 36:39.050
physicians and surgeons.

36:39.090 --> 36:40.090
We all need to pass

36:40.120 --> 36:42.000
the examination for the qualifications of medical practitioners.

36:42.620 --> 36:44.620
To put it simply,

36:44.640 --> 36:45.750
many anesthetists

36:45.780 --> 36:46.580
were nurses before.

36:46.600 --> 36:47.670
So they're different

36:47.710 --> 36:48.400
from us anesthesiologists.

36:48.470 --> 36:49.310
For example, in the hospital,

36:49.330 --> 36:50.670
if you

36:50.700 --> 36:51.870
call us anesthesiologists "anesthetists,"

36:51.890 --> 36:53.420
we'll correct you seriously

36:53.450 --> 36:54.730
that you should call us anesthesiologists.

36:56.870 --> 36:57.450
Indeed.

36:57.480 --> 36:59.360
Back in school, our teacher said

36:59.520 --> 37:01.190
anesthesiologists are the most knowledgeable.

37:01.430 --> 37:02.360
Whether it's internal medicine

37:02.390 --> 37:03.230
or surgery,

37:03.420 --> 37:04.470
anesthesiologists can manage both.

37:04.630 --> 37:05.860
Well,

37:05.880 --> 37:06.940
this is still a bit exaggerated,

37:06.970 --> 37:08.750
After all, everyone is a master in his own special field.

37:10.170 --> 37:11.900
And this part.

37:12.070 --> 37:14.260
About helping patients wake up after surgery.

37:14.710 --> 37:16.550
For us,

37:16.660 --> 37:17.530
after

37:17.950 --> 37:19.440
a patient wakes up,

37:19.470 --> 37:20.430
what we care about more is

37:20.450 --> 37:22.320
the patient's vitals,

37:22.350 --> 37:24.100
and if he or she has really waken up.

37:24.130 --> 37:25.610
But I can understand what you want to express.

37:25.630 --> 37:27.760
You want to write it as a false alarm.

37:28.150 --> 37:30.000
I think you can change it to

37:30.140 --> 37:31.800
the patient waking up repeatedly.

37:31.840 --> 37:33.040
Wake up repeatedly?

37:33.430 --> 37:34.280
Is that okay?

37:34.390 --> 37:35.000
Yes.

37:35.020 --> 37:36.210
It really happened.

37:37.090 --> 37:39.200
Once after a surgery,

37:39.230 --> 37:40.310
I woke up the patient.

37:40.330 --> 37:42.530
He asked me

37:42.780 --> 37:43.560
what time it was,

37:43.630 --> 37:45.230
and whether he could eat.

37:45.250 --> 37:45.950
I told him

37:45.950 --> 37:47.110
it was only 3 p.m.

37:47.130 --> 37:48.150
He said,

37:48.180 --> 37:49.390
I'll sleep for a bit longer then.

37:49.500 --> 37:50.560
And he fell asleep.

37:50.580 --> 37:51.710
I repeatedly

37:51.730 --> 37:53.480
tried to wake him up

37:53.670 --> 37:54.440
five times

37:54.490 --> 37:56.030
before he finally woke up.

37:56.050 --> 37:57.330
So it was actually...

37:57.480 --> 37:58.760
Quite scary.

37:59.200 --> 38:00.650
That's kind of crazy.

38:07.100 --> 38:08.170
Are you off work?

38:08.350 --> 38:09.110
Can we talk

38:09.150 --> 38:10.330
if you have time?

38:17.110 --> 38:18.250
Do you have work to do?

38:18.500 --> 38:20.000
How about I drive you back to the hospital?

38:21.870 --> 38:22.570
It's okay.

38:23.790 --> 38:24.920
Let's finish

38:24.950 --> 38:25.550
the script first.

38:27.760 --> 38:28.540
Dr. Lu.

38:28.560 --> 38:29.430
Please help me check

38:29.430 --> 38:31.020
the third scene of Episode 16.

38:31.050 --> 38:32.480
Does my wording make sense?

39:14.390 --> 39:15.270
Sorry,

39:15.590 --> 39:16.790
the subscriber you dialed

39:16.810 --> 39:18.170
cannot be connected at the moment.

39:18.310 --> 39:19.560
Please redial later.

39:19.590 --> 39:20.110
Sorry...

39:27.260 --> 39:36.620
[Entrecote]

39:28.990 --> 39:30.030
Let me give you a ride.

39:30.170 --> 39:31.900
No need. The car I called has arrived.

39:32.880 --> 39:34.460
You helped me all night.

39:34.540 --> 39:35.370
I'm a little embarrassed

39:35.380 --> 39:36.430
that I couldn't treat you to dinner.

39:37.790 --> 39:38.340
It's okay.

39:38.360 --> 39:39.590
You still have a chance.

39:40.430 --> 39:41.230
Really?

39:42.160 --> 39:43.480
We still have a chance?

39:48.030 --> 39:48.710
Don't get me wrong.

39:48.760 --> 39:49.640
I mean,

39:49.670 --> 39:50.960
don't tell me you don't have time

39:50.980 --> 39:52.600
when I want to treat you to dinner next time.

39:53.480 --> 39:54.140
I won't.

39:54.390 --> 39:55.440
I’m leaving then.

39:59.280 --> 40:00.240
Be careful.

40:00.260 --> 40:01.420
Text me when you get home.

40:14.990 --> 40:16.510
We definitely have a chance.

40:24.640 --> 40:32.010
[Sure.]

40:24.640 --> 40:32.010
[Are you off work? Can we talk?]

40:31.940 --> 40:32.620
Sure.
